Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍界大战开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蚂蚁们也很卖命嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们正饿着肚子等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小泽 你在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家憋不住了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代表木叶的精锐忍者们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组成了五大国有史以来的第一支忍者联军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴血奋战在第四次忍界大战的战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们时刻担心着家人的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎能守护我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们同样是战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每当忍界大战爆发之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会出现秃鹫一般的鼠辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击防御薄弱的村子 抢夺财物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们留守人员更要团结一致…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙从来都是吃不了兜着走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是鹿丸哥哥的妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有魄力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别小看我们妈妈组成的娘子军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱姐姐的妈妈也干劲十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人会提心吊胆地跑到村里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 井野妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止 确实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可也该考虑一下突发的特殊情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,匹敌晓的强盗们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会突然出现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得我想在留守期间给大家打气…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在嘀咕什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一如既往就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像平常那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢笑 哭泣 发怒 继续欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后用笑脸迎接老公们凯旋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能一如既往地生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下去吧 黑眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样真的能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真像惠比寿老师所言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不速之客袭击村子的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:04:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是想想没能出征的我们是多么无能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 早点出生就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡濑好帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 保护村子也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,功名祗向马上取
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看门可没人会嘉奖你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是爷爷 会怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷是火影 肯定会赶赴沙场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是否拥有火之意志呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火之意志…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想守护这个村子的强烈意志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护村子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才妈妈拜托我去村子东侧的山里采药
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有奇怪的忍者在森林中奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 木叶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害啊 有一百多人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百名忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 乌冬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说嘛 木叶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去东边的森林采蘑菇时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等前往战场的人凯旋时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让他们吃上美味的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 将这美味的蘑菇烧得脆脆的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烫烫烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里成了火焰般的地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是忍不住了 先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个火候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火属性的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且相当厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子的西边…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 这次换西边了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很大很大的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨忍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨忍是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是巨大的忍者啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和没说差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在村子的东边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又到东边了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有操纵螺旋丸的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人哥哥回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能 骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够使用螺旋丸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:08.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已过世的只有四代和自来也大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着的只有鸣人大哥和我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是用脚使出螺旋丸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用脚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用脚来踢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要使出浑身解数才能用手使出螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然用脚踢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是诅咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子正遭受尾兽的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾…尾兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾兽啊…尾兽再次前来袭击村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 您是在哪儿看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东方的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是尾兽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这回的尾兽是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先整理下至今为止收集到的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子的东边 不对 西边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说村子的附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算出现了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些大婶们也会赶跑他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着增强凝聚力才那样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮不到我出场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸 别再偷懒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快去修炼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修炼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨 即将有坏人来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨忍集团趁大部队出征 前来偷袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口吐火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还将螺旋丸传来传去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还和熊一起来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大人们靠不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子就由我们年轻人守护到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再摆出一副火影的架子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是三代的孙子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好 以后凭实力说话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人大哥也是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校里曾是拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今则是村子的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.89,0:12:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是下一任火影的不二人选
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼爹的时代已经过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战场上立下的功劳才能决定胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守卫村子根本不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:12:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自以为是的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.39,0:13:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 打就打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想要守护这个村子的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有火之意志的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎能成为火影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想让你受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我被苦无刺中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤的就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才拼命不让自己受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论发生什么事 我都会保护村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使只有我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸 去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊 木叶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萌黄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在这附近看见的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是在这附近看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿越树枝的忍者们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喷射火焰的火属性忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用脚操纵螺旋丸的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾兽熊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.07,0:15:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是幻影马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近刚从雾之国逃难至木叶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草木皆兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然会把马戏团给看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真糟糕 就我一个人大惊小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脸丢大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸 正如你所说 那些家伙出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那不过是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然从西边的森林…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 渡濑喊你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是继忍者 武士之后的第三势力 力士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座村庄就由我横纲大人收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力士是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西边的森林里有一大堆巨人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子的西边…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很大很大的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来 只有这个情报是真实的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡濑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着 我这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家之主都奔赴战场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁他们不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子的东西都归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还有这种败类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:17:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管孩子他爸们在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座村子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我们娘子军的火之意志来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞎扯什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让这些婆娘们见识见识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.06,0:18:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对拥有火之意志的人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里所有的人都像家人一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要守护家人的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能将村民们的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.33,0:18:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得更紧密 更强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股火之意志如果能遍布所有村民的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论村里发生什么 都能否极泰来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 这就是真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤…撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.80,0:19:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真碍事 快让开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是木叶丸厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火之意志 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 就将木叶丸高高举起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井野和老公都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就吃昨天的剩菜剩饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才懒得给闲在家里的老公做饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就将中午吃剩下的拿过来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.11,0:20:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶丸才是我们的头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人大哥算个啥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是神清气爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 先让鸣人过去吧 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要去的话 我先杀了鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来为他做担保 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何要这么帮他 蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.25,0:22:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使拳脚相交
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都无法看透我的内心吗 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.63,0:22:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集「火影忍者 疾风传」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:22:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「秘话·最强组合」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我来说是…
